OL,3,CStubHub fined #889,000 over 'hidden'
OL,4,Cticket fees and ordered to refund fans
OL,6,FStubHub has been fined #889,200 and
OL,7,Fordered to refund thousands of
OL,8,Fcustomers over "hidden" ticket fees.
OL,10,FThe Competition and Markets Authority
OL,11,F(CMA) was investigating the platform
OL,12,Fas part of a drive to clamp down on
OL,13,Fillegal and unfair online pricing
OL,14,Fpractices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
