CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782202689
OL,3,CStubHub fined #889,000 over 'hidden'
OL,4,Cticket fees and ordered to refund fans
OL,6,FIt found that the live event ticket
OL,7,Fmarketplace was using an illegal
OL,8,Fpractice known as drip pricing, which
OL,9,Fcan cause fans to be caught out by
OL,10,Fextra charges and means they may not
OL,11,Fhave had a chance to accurately
OL,12,Fcompare prices between sellers.
OL,14,FStubHub will have to refund more than
OL,15,F50,000 customers with an average
OL,16,Fpayout of #10.33.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
