FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782202689
OL,3,CStubHub fined #889,000 over 'hidden'
OL,4,Cticket fees and ordered to refund fans
OL,6,FBetween April 5 and December 7 2025,
OL,7,Fsome customers were required to pay
OL,8,Fmandatory costs such as delivery and
OL,9,Fservice fees when they purchased a
OL,10,Fticket on the platform.
OL,12,FBut the charges were applied at the
OL,13,Ffinal stage of the checkout process
OL,14,Fand not given upfront at the start,
OL,15,Fthe CMA found.
OL,17,FEmma Cochrane, executive director of
OL,18,Fconsumer protection at the CMA, said:
OL,19,F"Hitting customers with hidden fees is
OL,20,Fillegal.
OL,26,@{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782202689
OL,3,CStubHub fined #889,000 over 'hidden'
OL,4,Cticket fees and ordered to refund fans
OL,6,F"It's not fair to draw people in with
OL,7,Fwhat looks like a good deal, only for
OL,8,Fthem to find the real price is higher
OL,9,Fwhen they get to the checkout due to
OL,10,Fextra charges that can't be avoided."
OL,12,FStubHub will contact the 51,350 fans
OL,13,Fabout their refund, which will be
OL,14,Fautomatically repaid onto the card
OL,15,Fused to purchase their tickets.
OL,17,FThe company immediately took steps to
OL,18,Fend the practice and worked with the
OL,19,FCMA during its investigation, the
OL,20,Fwatchdog said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@eO]
