SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782202689
OL,3,CStubHub fined #889,000 over 'hidden'
OL,4,Cticket fees and ordered to refund fans
OL,6,FIt also admitted to breaking the law
OL,7,Fand agreed to settle the case early,
OL,8,Fmeaning it qualified for a 40%
OL,9,Freduction on the fine.
OL,11,FThe CMA is also investigating rival
OL,12,Fsecondary ticket website Viagogo over
OL,13,Fconcerns about hidden fees and will
OL,14,Fshare an update later in the summer.
OL,16,FThe regulator has been probing eight
OL,17,Fcompanies in total since November last
OL,18,Fyear over their online pricing
OL,19,Fpractices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
